parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear wheel hub can cause the vehicle to vibrate while leaning into a turn, which can lead to loss of control and increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle vibrates when leaning into a turn
fractures or cracks appear on the rear wheel hub.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Intermittent Engine Stalling at Low RPM and Speed
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent stalling of the engine at low RPM and speed can cause the motorcycle to lose power and control, increasing the risk of accidents and bodily injury.
symptoms: The engine spits and sputters
the motorcycle cuts off
leaving the driver with no control
the issue occurs frequently at low RPM and speed
the motorcycle is unable to maintain power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear wheel hub assembly can cause the vehicle to wobble excessively, leading to loss of control and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Noise coming from the rear wheels
excessive wobbling of the vehicle
possible wheel bearing failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Inadequate wheel bearings can cause the vehicle to vibrate or wobble, leading to loss of control and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Noise coming from the rear wheels
excessive wobbling of the vehicle
possible wheel bearing failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of a suspension component can cause the vehicle to pull to one side, making it difficult to control, which can lead to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: A loud sound is heard as if something has broken off the vehicle
the vehicle pulls to one side abnormally
the vehicle is difficult to control
especially when turning or exiting a highway.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Clutch and Rear Brake Vibration and Noise
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vibration and noise from the clutch and rear brake can cause driver distraction, loss of vehicle control, and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: Vibrations felt through the clutch pedal
vibrations felt through the seat or floor
loud grinding or screeching noise from the clutch or rear brake
unusual sounds when shifting gears or applying the brakes.
